<p>Reaching the edge of virtual worlds is something that fascinates me, so this feels like a good opportunity to point you towards the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FM9CqgIve_o">Red Dead Redemption 2-related short film The Grannies</a>, in which a group of players exploit a crack in the game's playing boundary and break through.</p>



